43 (b)(c) Upon adoption or promulgation of any emergency rule or regulation pursuant to
44 subsection (b) of this Code section, a majority of the State Election Board shall certify in
45 writing that such emergency rule or regulation was made in strict and exact compliance
46 with the provisions of this chapter and subsection (e) of Code Section 50-13-4.
47 (c)(d) In the event of any conflict between this Code section and any provision of
